OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother hot or very hot day for
OL,6,Fmost, with daytime temperatures widely
OL,7,Fabove average. Dry and predominantly
OL,8,Fclear with some hazy sunshine in the
OL,9,Fmorning. Wind remaining light for most.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FGenerally clear skies with
OL,12,Fsome occasional thin high cloud at
OL,13,Ftimes. A northeasterly breeze develops
OL,14,Fbringing low cloud and patchy fog onto
OL,15,Fthe coast and into eastern areas by
OL,16,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,171,160,301,260,100,100
